trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType" /> class represents the type on which the XML Web service is based.
The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> on which this XML Web service is based.
A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WebServiceProtocols" /> value that specifies the transmission protocols that are used to decrypt data sent in the XML Web service request.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType" /> class.
The key associated with the desired duplicate <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />.
Returns the duplicate <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associated with the specified key.
The duplicate <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associated with the specified key.
The key associated with the desired <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />.
Returns the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associated with the specified key.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associated with the specified key.
Returns a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> that indicates whether SOAP data transmissions sent to and from this XML Web service are encoded by default.
<see langword="true" /> if SOAP data transmissions sent to and from this XML Web service are encoded by default; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se le trasmissioni di dati inviate da e verso il servizio Web XML sono codificati per impostazione predefinita. in caso contrario, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the namespace to which this XML Web service belongs.
A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the namespace to which this XML Web service belongs.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.String" /> che contiene lo spazio dei nomi a cui appartiene questo servizio Web XML.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> that indicates whether SOAP messages that are routed to this XML Web service are routed based on the <see langword="SOAPAction" /> HTTP header.
<see langword="true" /> if SOAP messages that are routed to this XML Web service are routed based on the <see langword="SOAPAction" /> HTTP header; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se i messaggi SOAP che vengono indirizzati al servizio Web XML vengono indirizzati in base il <see langword="SOAPAction" /> intestazione HTTP in caso contrario, <see langword="false" />.
